title: Exception thrown when exporting data in a table inside a grid cell
description: When attempting to export data in a table that is inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown. This issue occurs when performing the export operation.
OB: When trying to export data in a table that is inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: Data should be successfully exported from a table that is inside a grid cell without any exceptions being thrown.
SR:
To reproduce this issue, follow these steps:
1. Insert a grid.
2. Insert a table into one of the grid cells.
3. Insert another table into the other grid cell.
4. Attempt to export the data from one of the tables within the grid.
